Text:
The torrent also has ZaRa and Merzbow wallpapers.

There is a folder called "-CD1" that you can just delete because it is "Seitaka" from "F.I.D.", which is already included in the "F.I.D." folder.

There is also a file "01-Ananga-Ranga.mp3" that you can delete because it is included already in the "Venereology" folder.

The albums "April 1992" and "Kamadhenu" will be added soon on seperate torrents.
